# Project rules — Astronautisté (astronautiste.cz)

# Auto-loaded by Zed editor (and other agents reading .rules). Source of truth for
# doctrines: .aiad/policies/  (index: .aiad/policies/INDEX.md). Enforced by .githooks/pre-commit.

Stack: Zola (static site) + Tailwind CSS ^3.4.17 + Flowbite ^2.5.2 + Alpine.js.
Build: scripts/build.sh. Default reply language: Czech; code identifiers in English.

## STRICT — Flowbite v2 / Tailwind v3 (.aiad/policies/flowbite-stack.policy.md)

This project uses Flowbite v2 / Tailwind v3 (JS config). You MUST:
- Use tailwind.config.js with darkMode:'class', require('flowbite/plugin'), and
  @tailwind base/components/utilities in styles/input.css.
- Use data-attribute components (data-collapse-toggle, etc.) with a11y attributes
  (aria-controls, aria-expanded, aria-hidden, sr-only). Site is dark-only (<html class="dark">).

You MUST NOT use Tailwind v4 / Flowbite v4 CSS-first syntax:
  @custom-variant, @plugin "flowbite", @import "tailwindcss", @theme {}
The pre-commit hook (Gate 5) blocks these in source files.

WARNING: flowbite.com llms.txt / llms-full.txt are now for v4 — DO NOT apply them here.

## Brand
Canonical tagline: „Myslíme na hvězdy, jednáme vědecky." Brand is always "Astronautisté",
domain "astronautiste.cz" (never "austronautiste"). Brand voice: messaging/.
